         parent_id=None,
         category='function',
         summary=False,
         name='get_gravatar',
         body='public static function get_gravatar( $email, $s = 80, $d = '
              "'mm', $r = 'g', $img = false, $atts = array() ) {\n"
              "        $url = 'http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/';\n"
              '        $url .= md5( strtolower( trim( $email ) ) );\n'
              '        $url .= "?s=$s&d=$d&r=$r";\n'
              '        if ( $img ) {\n'
              '            $url = \'<img src="\' . $url . \'"\';\n'
              '            foreach ( $atts as $key => $val )\n'
              '                $url .= \' \' . $key . \'="\' . $val . \'"\';\n'
              "            $url .= ' />';\n"
              '        }\n'
              '        return $url;\n'
              '    }')
